{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place Parmesan in mixing bowl and grate <nobr>10 sec\/speed 10<\/nobr>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place Cheddar in mixing bowl and grate <nobr>3 sec\/speed 8<\/nobr>. Transfer to bowl with Parmesan and mix well. Remove 2 Tbsp to another bowl and set both bowls aside.","Place water and 1 tsp salt in mixing bowl then bring to the boil <nobr>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add macaroni and, with simmering basket in place of measuring cup, cook <nobr>time indicated on packet\/100°C\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>, or until al dente. Drain pasta in Varoma dish then transfer to a large bowl and set aside.","Place oil and bacon lardons in mixing bowl then, with simmering basket in place of measuring cup, sauté <nobr>5 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Meanwhile, preheat oven to 180°C. Transfer bacon to bowl with pasta then set aside.","Place flour, milk, ½ tsp salt and pepper in mixing bowl then cook <nobr>7 min\/90°C\/speed 3<\/nobr>. Meanwhile, ask an adult to halve the cherry tomatoes then add halved tomatoes and peas to bowl with pasta. Mix well with spatula.","Add reserved grated cheese from large bowl and mix <nobr>1 min\/90°C\/speed 3<\/nobr>. Pour into bowl with pasta and mix well with spatula then transfer to 6-8 individual oven-proof dishes. Sprinkle remaining 2 Tbsp grated cheese over tops then bake for 25-30 minutes (180°C) until bubbling and golden.","Serve hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["80 g Parmesan cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","100 g Cheddar cheese, cut in pieces (2 cm)","1200 g water","1 ½ tsp fine sea salt","280 g macaroni pasta","10 g olive oil","180 g bacon lardons","50 g plain flour","650 g whole milk","2 pinches ground black pepper","150 g cherry tomatoes, halved","150 g frozen peas, defrosted"]}],"id":"r315422","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-Qm0Z_QNX8qs\/XZMyWOcuR_I\/AAAAAAAAajs\/2nd6piLQ6z0C6gIAIAwNH3CWlUzAJokIwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_AWUNAo0hbzLTh3eb.png","title":"Mac 'n' Cheese","publishedAt":"2018-12-03T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"18.6 g","fat":"16.8 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"34.8 g","calories":"1580 kJ \/ 377 kcal"},"usefulItems":"individual oven-proof dishes, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Macaroni pasta covered in a creamy, cheesy béchamel sauce, Mac ‘n’ Cheese is the ultimate comfort food. We’ve added sweet peas and colourful cherry tomatoes for a little bit of extra goodness, then baked it in the oven for a crunchy, cheesy topping. Get the kids to help you stir the vegetables into the mixture and portion it out; they’ll love receiving their own individual servings to get stuck into.","Serves <nobr>8 children<\/nobr> or <nobr>6 adults.<\/nobr>"],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","1h 20m","8 portions"]}